Where to Watch

In this quirky crime comedy, novice criminal Henry (Keanu Reeves) and a veteran con artist (James Caan) try to rob a bank connected to a theater by an underground tunnel. As part of the plan, Henry lands a role in a play being produced at the theater. However, their scheme falls apart when he begins to fall in love with his costar. Directed by Malcolm Venville.
